name: Kathy Gray, 52
description: Gray is a transsexual woman who has been undergoing transition for four years while struggling with off-and-on homelessness.
videocaption: Kathy Gray talks about being homeless.

name: Oscar McKinney, 50
description: Homeless for at least 20 years, McKinney works odd jobs while living in tents.
videocaption: Oscar McKinney talks about being homeless.

name: Robert Brownell, 58, and Cassandra Brownell, 64
description: The Brownells are married and retired — he from working with flooring, she from bartending — and consider their RV camper their rolling home.
videocaption: Robert Brownell talks about being homeless.

name: Angelique Mayweather, 48
description: Mayweather worked at catering jobs until abusive relationships led to homelessness two years ago.
videocaption: Angelique Mayweather talks about being homeless.

name: Papa Smirf, 57
description: He refuses to give his real name — has been homeless off and on in San Francisco for nearly four decades.
videocaption: Papa Smirf talks about being homeless.

name: Terry Quinn, 54
description: Quinn, who had been homeless off and on for eight years, struggled with methamphetamine addiction and is now working toward sobriety.
videocaption: Terry Quinn talks about being homeless.
